Media Access Group at WGBH

44:13.685 --> 44:15.987
You've answered the call
on 9-1-1.

44:16.021 --> 44:18.256
Now here are a few more shows
to check out from Fox.

44:20.658 --> 44:21.860
Buckle up, buttercup.

44:24.195 --> 44:26.531
It's real, and it pulls
people together.

44:26.564 --> 44:30.135
-* We're breaking waves
shooting star *
-(siren wailing)

44:30.168 --> 44:33.705
* We live for glory
not forever *

44:33.739 --> 44:34.740
MAN: Touchdown!

44:34.773 --> 44:38.343
* Reach out *

44:38.376 --> 44:41.980
* Make this right here
right now *

44:42.013 --> 44:44.916
* Stand up *

44:45.784 --> 44:47.552
* Here right now *

44:47.585 --> 44:49.554
That sounds like fun.
